quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  75,20,"Shikali kario tawe! Halali enywe mwayanza obulamu bwokhushialo."
  75,21,"Ne mulekhanga obulamu bwomwikulu."
  75,22,"Obweni inyanga eyo bulimesamesa."
  75,23,"Buliheenga Nyasaye wabwo Omulesi."
  75,24,"Ne obweni bundi inyanga eyo bulisinyikha po."
  75,25,"Bulimanya mbu buulilwe nende shifunakanga olukongofuma."
  75,26,"Shikali kario tawe! Olwa omwoyo kuliula khushikumba shielikosi."
  75,27,"Mana kareebwe mbu: “Ni wina umusilikha?”"
  75,28,"Ne omwene namanya mbu toto bwene okho nikho okhufwa."
  75,29,"Ne olwa emiluku chilitilana halala okundi khukundi."
  75,30,"Inyanga eyo niyo yebindu bioosi biliyilwa ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi."
  75,31,"Mana shiyafuchilila (aka Nyasaye), nohomba shiyaswaliya tawe."
  75,32,"Halali yakatsula mana nafutara."
  75,33,"Mana natsia khubandu baye niyesunga."
  75,34,"Oh abaane koo ewe! Oh abaane koo ewe!"
  75,35,"Mana khandi oh abaane koo ewe! Oh abaane koo ewe!"
  75,36,"Koo, omundu aparanga mbu anyala okhulekhwa butswa eshikhaya?"
  75,37,"Koo, shiyali indonyande yamatsi kolwibulo kamitsungwa tawe?"
  75,38,"Mana naba amalika, mana Nyasaye namuloonga namukaasia obulayi muno."
  75,39,"Mana nakhola okhurulanamwo tsimbia tsibili: abasatsa nende abakhasi."
  75,40,"Kho koo, oyo shali omunyali muno wokhulamusia abafu tawe?"
  76,1,"Toto biabura ebise ebirambi khumundu, olwa yaali naalali eshindu shirumbulwa tawe."
  76,2,"Toto efwe khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende imwo yobulamu, yesasania, (yomusatsa nende omukhasi) khulwokhumutema, kho nikhumukholaye okhuwulila muno, nende okhulola po."
  76,3,"Toto efwe khwamulunjisia kunjira ilunjifu, niyenya asubire Nyasaye mana abe wokhupa orio, nohomba alonde khunjira ya obukhayi (alobe injira ya Nyasaye)."
  76,4,"Toto efwe khwarecheshela Abakhayi eminyororo, nende tsirimba nende omulilo omululu."
  76,5,"Toto Abandu abalayi balinywa eshinywebwa shiasasibwamwo ‘kafura’."